{"tid":2116770,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐","createTime":"2020-07-20T11:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T13:36:27.000Z","uid":260581,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"339a78d8dd4e84f72c56b9423723aaabd174e1fd","tid":2116770,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T11:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWswPpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWswPpt.jpg&h=7d5cf735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早排有人問我點整 所以我上次整東坡肉嗰陣買咗2kg <br />\n今次又係拎一部份出嚟煮<br />\n煮之前我先插左佢幾野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5huy2K8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5huy2K8.jpg&h=71548ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0gd2LT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0gd2LT.jpg&h=50eb9992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先凍水落煲 水滾出水10分鐘<br />\n大家可以加啲 薑蔥紹酒落去<br />\n我冇加係我唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就可以浸冰水15分鐘<br />\n跟住洗乾淨舊肉同除毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9x1sdQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9x1sdQ.jpg&h=8a5f43fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qiPORFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqiPORFw.jpg&h=648f3509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先將舊肉係個底改幾刀<br />\n方便你醃同煮熟後斬<br />\n<br />\n醃料我用左Vodka同少少生抽<br />\n粉就有少少五香粉 鹽同糖<br />\n用Vodka係因為我呢邊買唔到玫瑰露<br />\n我第一次整嘅時候用過紹酒<br />\n想試吓有冇唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太家可以一次過將啲醃料撈起佢 然後先醃<br />\n但係上次咁整個人認為太重口味 所以我選擇搽上去<br />\n醃料我亦冇用曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住唔好醃埋個皮 個皮唔好醃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vXT2MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vXT2MA.jpg&h=1ed35a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後拎豬皮插起勢咁插<br />\n記住要拎廚房紙一路抹返乾身佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇插既朋友仔可以去上海街買返個<br />\n或者用竹籤or叉都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nheK9ub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnheK9ub.jpg&h=bf8c6a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAwEYnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAwEYnx.jpg&h=ccaa6fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住就可以搽少少白醋上皮<br />\n放入雪櫃風乾 醃佢至少4個鐘<br />\n我就放過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今朝起身我又再搽多少少白醋<br />\n記住戴返住手套先整 唔係全日隻手臭到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JiDuvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JiDuvw.jpg&h=31caa85f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入焗爐前先用少少水撈落d粗鹽到<br />\n然後鋪面 <br />\n焗爐預熱200度 先焗25分鐘<br />\n時間溫度視乎舊肉大小 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iR7EdXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiR7EdXG.jpg&h=eb93a03d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n焗25分鐘後拎出 焗爐再升到250度<br />\n上鐵架再焗到個皮脆就ok<br />\n落少少水落鹽既原因係抽乾水後<br />\n你可以成塊拎起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我亦再插多幾野 再用廚房紙抹乾啲油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZXpp5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZXpp5n.jpg&h=9efc4fde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9xHWb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9xHWb4.jpg&h=bdc4f937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n焗完放10分鐘先切<br />\n係我on9 焗完唔記得影完成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幾脆自己聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://imgur.com/gallery/2FvJxlk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fgallery%2F2FvJxlk&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=e357b25f\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/gallery/2FvJxlk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/gallery/LKsLsG6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fgallery%2FLKsLsG6&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=5e2f4844\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/gallery/LKsLsG6</a>"},{"pid":"1644652dd9556b6bde8b4f88e0dfbeb27d20d4e0","tid":2116770,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"搶香先 keep住支持"},{"pid":"4c80c59a1a341b287c0c1f93cb0ea1c95f6f964f","tid":2116770,"uid":260581,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVoDuzM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVoDuzM.jpg&h=f4302995&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ua4ZYs7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fua4ZYs7.jpg&h=660eea06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAUbPzP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAUbPzP.jpg&h=7eb61ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撚廚"},{"pid":"6b8e7224c8487b51cf32043b140cec563a2be2d4","tid":2116770,"uid":345300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339a78d8dd4e84f72c56b9423723aaabd174e1fd","tid":2116770,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T11:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWswPpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWswPpt.jpg&h=7d5